Harper Carter https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Harper_Carter 0 William Harper Carter (born in August 15, 1939) is an American entrepreneur and former actor. After his retirement from cinema, Carter changed careers and is currently an Executive Vice President of a real estate company.
